Klopp on Robertson: &quot;He is cool. He played outstandingly well at Hull but people have said &lsquo;In defensive one-on-ones he is not that good.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;That&rsquo;s not a problem. I can teach him how to deal with one-on-ones because I could do that and I was a really bad footballer.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;I&rsquo;m not interested in what Jose Mourinho says. Why should I talk about Manchester United? Jose is talking about us, yes.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Sorry that we lost the final yes, that&rsquo;s right. We played Sevilla, they played Ajax. That's the difference.&quot;

Henderson on Lallana: &quot;He's a massive player for us. Not only on the pitch, but as a person off the field.&quot;<br />
<br />
Henderson on Lallana: &quot;He was one of the best players in the league really. I'm not just saying then because he's my mate!&quot;
